        {
            "title": "韓國股市初段跌逾2%　失守7000點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">韓國股市今日初段顯著受壓，首爾綜合指數失守7,000點關口，較早時報6,930點，下跌166點，跌幅達2.35%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16425934-%e9%9f%93%e5%9c%8b%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be2%e3%80%80%e5%a4%b1%e5%ae%887000%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/07/20260722_FI_source-ap_KS.jpg.webp",
